  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frontera is primarily a fantasy city builder with emphasis on producing items for unit wants and combat. Units have four stats trainable at buildings that will also sell technology. Available items and production will grow strong enough to challenge the monsters that infest the rest of the island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Establish production chains to make over 90 items. Gather raw resources to refine them into tools, weapons, and amenities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/8d5acd1eac370adad2aa1916f7985852.poster.avif?t=1762531764\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/8d5acd1eac370adad2aa1916f7985852.webm?t=1762531764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/8d5acd1eac370adad2aa1916f7985852.mp4?t=1762531764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Store  products and settlers will make purchases at the markets. Look into the wants of your people to see what they will buy. Fulfill unit wants to a satisfactory amount to increase the rate that more will arrive to help. Units will also purchase new tools to use at work. Collect income from these purchases and from housing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/643b7ab91f6ee85cae7be088c81f30f3.poster.avif?t=1762531764\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/643b7ab91f6ee85cae7be088c81f30f3.webm?t=1762531764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/643b7ab91f6ee85cae7be088c81f30f3.mp4?t=1762531764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/1badfae1241c51fa05987ec9ec2be8f5.poster.avif?t=1762531764\" width=616 height=50 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/1badfae1241c51fa05987ec9ec2be8f5.webm?t=1762531764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/1badfae1241c51fa05987ec9ec2be8f5.mp4?t=1762531764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your collected funds to attract more settlers and license technology from the guilds. Build and upgrade guild buildings to train your units to be more efficient at production.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/9519f30ed25ab44ebc1465ed37847e73.poster.avif?t=1762531764\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/9519f30ed25ab44ebc1465ed37847e73.webm?t=1762531764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/9519f30ed25ab44ebc1465ed37847e73.mp4?t=1762531764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit an army to establish and defend outposts that will grant passive resource generation. Units will automatically fight once they meet an enemy on the overworld.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/07a3e223a6f34af39bea3803731e78e7.poster.avif?t=1762531764\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/07a3e223a6f34af39bea3803731e78e7.webm?t=1762531764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/07a3e223a6f34af39bea3803731e78e7.mp4?t=1762531764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/02902718defbd4213e82d98f4822f480.poster.avif?t=1762531764\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/02902718defbd4213e82d98f4822f480.webm?t=1762531764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/02902718defbd4213e82d98f4822f480.mp4?t=1762531764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make your way to deal with the source of the islands monster infestation, after which the island will be secured!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frontera is primarily a fantasy city builder with emphasis on producing items for unit wants and combat. Units have four stats trainable at buildings that will also sell technology. Available items and production will grow strong enough to challenge the monsters that infest the rest of the island.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Establish production chains to make over 90 items. Gather raw resources to refine them into tools, weapons, and amenities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/8d5acd1eac370adad2aa1916f7985852.poster.avif?t=1762531764\" width=616 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/8d5acd1eac370adad2aa1916f7985852.webm?t=1762531764\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/8d5acd1eac370adad2aa1916f7985852.mp4?t=1762531764\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Store  products and settlers will make purchases at the markets. Look into the wants of your people to see what they will buy. Fulfill unit wants to a satisfactory amount to increase the rate that more will arrive to help. Units will also purchase new tools to use at work. Collect income from these purchases and from housing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2393630/extras/643b7ab91f6ee85cae7be088c81f30f3.poster.avif?t=1762531764\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com